message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.NEURON - The paper involves the use of deep learning for automatic segmentation of lumbosacral structures on CT images, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) domains. Additionally, the study has medical applications and involves the segmentation of nerves, which could potentially fall under the medical imaging (cs.MED) and neuroscience (cs.NEURON) categories.
